sonusH323SignallingMIB.description: The MIB Module for H323 IP Call Signal Channel Management.

sonusH323SigSrvTimerT301.name: sonusH323SigSrvTimerT301
sonusH323SigSrvTimerT301.description: The T301 timer (in seconds). This value applies to all calls.

sonusH323SigSrvTimerT303.name: sonusH323SigSrvTimerT303
sonusH323SigSrvTimerT303.description: The T303 call timer (in seconds). This value applies to all calls.

sonusH323SigSrvTimerT310.name: sonusH323SigSrvTimerT310
sonusH323SigSrvTimerT310.description: The T310 timer (in seconds). This value applies to all calls.

sonusH323SigTimerEstablish.name: sonusH323SigTimerEstablish
sonusH323SigTimerEstablish.description: The H225 signal channel establishment timer (in seconds.) This value applies to all signal channels.

sonusH323SigTimerTcpConnect.name: sonusH323SigTimerTcpConnect
sonusH323SigTimerTcpConnect.description: The TCP connect timer (in seconds). This applies to all signal channels.

sonusH323H225PortIpAddress.name: sonusH323H225PortIpAddress
sonusH323H225PortIpAddress.description: IP Address of the H225 call signaling port - this is a required parameter.

sonusH323H225PortNum.name: sonusH323H225PortNum
sonusH323H225PortNum.description: TCP port number of the H225 call signaling port (default is H323 registered port 1720).

sonusH323H225PortShelfId.name: sonusH323H225PortShelfId
sonusH323H225PortShelfId.description: The shelf number of the PNS board providing the H225 connection service. 0 means not configured.

sonusH323H225PortSlotNum.name: sonusH323H225PortSlotNum
sonusH323H225PortSlotNum.description: The slot number of the PNS board providing the H225 connection service. 0 means not configured.

sonusH323H245PortIpAddress.name: sonusH323H245PortIpAddress
sonusH323H245PortIpAddress.description: IP Address of the H245 port - this is a required parameter.

sonusH323H245PortShelfId.name: sonusH323H245PortShelfId
sonusH323H245PortShelfId.description: The shelf number of the PNS board providing the H245 connection service. 0 means not configured.

sonusH323H245PortSlotNum.name: sonusH323H245PortSlotNum
sonusH323H245PortSlotNum.description: The slot number of the PNS board providing the H225 connection service. 0 means not configured.

sonusH323SignalingControlMode.name: sonusH323SignalingControlMode
sonusH323SignalingControlMode.description: This object controls the mode of H323 service.

sonusH323SignalingControlState.name: sonusH323SignalingControlState
sonusH323SignalingControlState.description: This object controls the state of H323 service.

sonusH323SignalingControlAction.name: sonusH323SignalingControlAction
sonusH323SignalingControlAction.description: This object controls to force all call drops or let the call finish during a time period, which is controled by sonusH323SigTimerDryupTimeout.

sonusH323SignalingControlDryupTimeout.name: sonusH323SignalingControlDryupTimeout
sonusH323SignalingControlDryupTimeout.description: This timer controls the time (in minutes) to wait to place the H323 into out of service state, when the dryup command is issued.

sonusH323FeCurrentStatIndex.name: sonusH323FeCurrentStatIndex

sonusH323FeCurrentStatStatus.description: The state of this H323 port current status.
